A given page on a website can have value in many different ways.

== News value ==

This occurs when a page covers a recent news event

Types of news value include:

* Update value: Providing incremental updates on an existing item that the reader has some prior knowledge of.

* Summary value: Providing a complete snapshot summary of a news event.

* Backgrounder and connections value: Providing more background, as well as connections to other events, for a news items.

== Reference value ==

Types of reference value:

* General info value

* Specific info value

* Link-to-others value

